Small description of change:

Implemented `switch-case` recognition for Volt. Introduced syntax:
```jinja
{% switch foo %}
    {% case 0 %}
    {% case 1 %}
    {% case 2 %}
        `foo` is less than 3 but not negative
        {% break %}
    {% case 3 %}
        `foo` is 3
        {% break %}
    {% default %}
        `foo` is {{ foo }}
{% endswitch %}
```

It is important to understand how the switch statement is executed in order to avoid mistakes.
The switch statement executes line by line (actually, statement by statement). This is why `break` is necessary in some cases.

**NOTE:** Any output (including whitespace) between a switch statement and the first case will result in a syntax error. This is the responsibility of the user. However, we can clear empty lines and whitespaces here to reduce the number of errors. For more see: http://php.net/control-structures.alternative-syntax

Thus, for example the Volt syntax:
```jinja
{% switch username %}
    {% case "Jim" %}
        Hello username
    {% case "Nik" %}
        {{ username }}!
        {% break %}
    {% default %}
        Who are you?
{% endswitch %}
```

will be compiled to:
```html+php
<?php switch ($username): ?>
<?php case 'Jim': ?>
Hello username
<?php case 'Nik': ?>
<?= $username ?>!
<?php break; ?>
<?php default: ?>
Who are you?
<?php endswitch ?>
```

--------

### Restrictions

##### `case` without `switch`


```jinja
 {% case EXPRESSION %}
```

Will trow Fatal error: `Uncaught Phalcon\Mvc\View\Exception: Unexpected CASE`.

--------

##### `switch` without `endswitch`


```jinja
 {% switch EXPRESSION %}
```

Will trow Fatal error: `Uncaught Phalcon\Mvc\View\Exception: Syntax error, unexpected EOF in ..., there is a 'switch' block without 'endswitch'`.

--------

##### `default` without `switch`

```jinja
 {% default %}
```

Will _not throw_ error because `default` is reserved word for filters like `{{ EXPRESSION | default(VALUE) }}` but _in this case_ the expression don't do anything - just empty char `''` .

--------

##### nested `switch`

```jinja
{% switch EXPRESSION %}
  {% switch EXPRESSION %}
  {% endswitch %}
{% endswitch %}
```

Will trow Fatal error: `Uncaught Phalcon\Mvc\View\Exception: A nested switch detected. There is no nested switch-case statements support in ... on line ...`.

--------

##### a `switch` without expression

```jinja
{% switch %}
  {% case EXPRESSION %}
      {% break %}
{% endswitch %}
```

Will trow Fatal error: `Uncaught Phalcon\Mvc\View\Exception: Syntax error, unexpected token %} in ... on line ...`.

--------

Thanks.

